Interface GridNode<D>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSplitDockGrid.Node

    public interface GridNode<D>
    A node of an AbstractSplitDockGrid, represents a stack of Dockables and their position.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
